WEBVTT

01:43.280 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:50.080 --> 01:51.560
- I couldn't stand it.
- Wait.

01:52.880 --> 01:54.840
- What were you doing?
- Let me eat first.

01:55.680 --> 01:56.600
What?

01:58.120 --> 01:59.640
The three of us were in a ranked match.

01:59.720 --> 02:01.240
Then I got a call.

02:01.320 --> 02:02.320
You even scolded me.

02:02.920 --> 02:04.760
- The day we almost won?
- Yes, that day.

02:06.840 --> 02:07.960
I told you before, didn't I?

02:08.039 --> 02:09.080
Her again?

02:09.639 --> 02:11.640
Valentine's Day was around the corner,

02:11.720 --> 02:12.760
so I bought her roses.

02:14.160 --> 02:15.520
That's so tacky.

02:16.800 --> 02:17.800
Is buying roses tacky?

02:18.720 --> 02:20.360
Yes, it's so tacky.

02:20.440 --> 02:22.280
Man, you have no game. Seriously.

02:22.360 --> 02:24.680
- All right. Eat.
- You don't get it.

02:24.760 --> 02:25.960
No amount of flowers will work.

02:26.040 --> 02:27.400
- Listen.
- What flowers did you give?

02:27.480 --> 02:29.560
- Don't you know?
- And it's extremely tacky.

02:29.640 --> 02:31.960
Do you know that he gave her red roses?

02:32.520 --> 02:33.520
You still don't remember.

02:33.600 --> 02:35.320
Can you pay more attention to me?

02:35.400 --> 02:36.280
Let me tell you.

02:36.360 --> 02:37.440
She posted on Weibo

02:37.520 --> 02:38.840
that it would be nice

02:38.920 --> 02:41.240
to receive red roses on Valentine's Day.

02:41.320 --> 02:42.720
I liked the post.

02:42.800 --> 02:45.200
Then I immediately went out
to get her red roses.

02:49.920 --> 02:51.160
I ate too much.

02:51.880 --> 02:53.480
We shouldn't have ordered so much food.

02:53.560 --> 02:55.280
We had already ordered before you came.

02:55.360 --> 02:57.320
Did he do all that

02:59.040 --> 03:01.120
because he didn't want me
to be embarrassed?

03:01.640 --> 03:02.840
One wanted your number.

03:02.920 --> 03:04.600
Another wanted your number.

03:04.680 --> 03:06.120
No one wanted mine.

03:06.200 --> 03:07.480
Am I not your backup?

03:07.560 --> 03:08.880
Just change your name to Sang Yan.

03:08.960 --> 03:10.120
Wouldn't you be yourself then?

03:10.600 --> 03:11.960
Or you can change it to Duan Jiaxu.

03:13.040 --> 03:14.480
Okay, I'll get the car.

03:14.560 --> 03:16.320
You two can wait for me at the entrance.

03:17.120 --> 03:17.960
Follow them.

03:18.760 --> 03:19.840
- Hurry.
- Let's go.

03:21.920 --> 03:23.320
Sang Zhi.

03:23.400 --> 03:24.960
Shall I take you to the claw machine?

03:25.040 --> 03:26.040
Let's play.

03:26.120 --> 03:27.320
No, thank you, Qian Fei.

03:27.400 --> 03:29.320
It's fine. I promised you. Come on.

03:29.400 --> 03:30.280
Listen, I'm the best.

03:30.360 --> 03:31.560
I'll teach you step by step.

03:38.720 --> 03:39.640
Sang Zhi.

03:40.120 --> 03:40.960
Take a handful.

03:41.960 --> 03:42.880
Thank you.

03:42.960 --> 03:43.800
Take it.

03:45.640 --> 03:46.520
This is enough.

03:46.600 --> 03:48.360
Okay, come on. I'll teach you.

04:16.560 --> 04:18.000
Here, let me help you.

04:51.200 --> 04:52.080
The white one?

05:09.320 --> 05:10.280
Give me two more.

05:30.560 --> 05:32.040
I got you a plushie.

05:32.120 --> 05:33.240
Don't cry anymore.

05:39.320 --> 05:40.520
Thank you, Jiaxu.

05:40.600 --> 05:41.480
Have some candy.

05:43.920 --> 05:45.160
What do you think?

05:45.240 --> 05:46.640
Wasn't I brave earlier?

05:48.360 --> 05:49.800
Thank you, Jiaxu.

05:49.880 --> 05:51.400
Come on. I'll see you home.

05:51.880 --> 05:53.800
I can lecture you along the way.

05:54.920 --> 05:55.760
Wait a second.

05:56.400 --> 05:58.560
When Sang Yan met the teacher,

05:58.640 --> 06:00.280
he didn't lecture me afterward.

06:01.040 --> 06:02.280
- Really?
- Really.

06:03.880 --> 06:05.440
I'll call your brother and ask him.

06:05.520 --> 06:06.760
No! Wait a minute!

06:06.840 --> 06:08.280
Won't he find out if you ask him?

06:08.360 --> 06:10.280
Then you will have come here for nothing!

06:10.360 --> 06:11.640
Kiddo.

06:11.720 --> 06:14.080
You called me all the way here.

06:14.160 --> 06:15.760
And now you're lying to me.

06:15.840 --> 06:17.240
Won't that make me a sucker?

06:25.240 --> 06:26.480
That again?

06:32.840 --> 06:34.200
Fine, I won't tell your brother.

06:35.880 --> 06:36.920
Kiddo.

06:39.520 --> 06:40.720
Goodbye then.

06:42.480 --> 06:43.360
Where are you going?

06:43.960 --> 06:45.920
It's getting late.

06:46.000 --> 06:46.840
If I'm not home yet,

06:46.920 --> 06:48.120
my mom will worry about me.

06:49.120 --> 06:50.200
I'll see you home.

06:51.040 --> 06:52.120
Wait!

06:52.200 --> 06:54.040
The bus station is nearby.

06:54.120 --> 06:56.640
Besides, it's a short walk
after I get off the bus.

06:56.720 --> 06:59.040
Jiaxu, you must be very busy right now.

07:00.120 --> 07:01.960
I've kept you long enough.

07:02.920 --> 07:04.040
I'll get out of your hair.

07:04.120 --> 07:05.800
You didn't care so much about me before.

07:06.440 --> 07:08.520
I'll see you home no matter how busy I am.

07:30.840 --> 07:31.680
Walk faster.

07:38.200 --> 07:39.800
Jiaxu, it's getting dark.

07:39.880 --> 07:41.320
Are you not returning to campus yet?

07:42.800 --> 07:44.280
Don't worry, kiddo.

07:44.360 --> 07:46.440
I will keep today's incident a secret.

07:46.960 --> 07:47.800
Really?

07:48.680 --> 07:49.600
Pinky promise?

07:54.800 --> 07:56.360
You must also promise me

07:56.440 --> 07:58.240
you'll pay attention in class

07:58.320 --> 07:59.600
and not break the school rules.

07:59.680 --> 08:01.040
- Okay?
- Okay.

08:03.320 --> 08:04.560
I'm not joking.

08:05.080 --> 08:06.360
If your teacher wants

08:06.440 --> 08:07.640
to meet your parents again,

08:07.720 --> 08:09.680
what happened today will be exposed.

08:09.760 --> 08:10.720
I'll be in trouble.

08:11.280 --> 08:12.520
You can come again next time.

08:13.440 --> 08:14.480
Will there be a next time?

08:15.320 --> 08:16.520
No.

08:16.600 --> 08:18.680
I just think you're very nice to me.

08:18.760 --> 08:20.480
You're nicer to me than my brother is.

08:20.560 --> 08:21.440
So…

08:22.600 --> 08:25.120
If something like this happens again,

08:26.000 --> 08:28.280
can I ask you to pretend to be my brother?

08:35.559 --> 08:36.440
Got it.

08:38.559 --> 08:39.679
Go home.

08:41.280 --> 08:42.840
There had better not be a next time.

08:48.840 --> 08:49.720
Here.

08:50.760 --> 08:51.600
By the way,

08:53.240 --> 08:54.880
the light bulb in your kitchen burnt out.

08:55.520 --> 08:56.720
After you get inside,

08:56.800 --> 08:57.880
give this to your dad.

08:57.960 --> 08:59.920
Okay. Thank you, Jiaxu.

09:00.000 --> 09:01.240
Don't mention it.

09:01.320 --> 09:02.200
Hurry inside.

09:05.960 --> 09:07.800
- Goodbye, Jiaxu.
- Be good.

09:08.880 --> 09:10.160
Bye.

09:54.600 --> 09:55.640
Difficult kiddo.

09:58.480 --> 09:59.760
Let's go.

10:21.680 --> 10:23.680
CHAPTER THREE, CONSIDERATE

10:23.760 --> 10:25.280
GET A LITTLE CLOSER

10:27.880 --> 10:29.480
Why did you lie to me again?

10:30.040 --> 10:32.000
I don't want to go. I really don't.

10:32.080 --> 10:33.840
We're already here. Let's go together.

10:33.920 --> 10:35.440
Besides, I already bought a gift.

10:36.000 --> 10:38.000
That's right. I didn't buy a gift.

10:38.080 --> 10:38.920
It doesn't matter.

10:39.000 --> 10:40.240
We'll say it's from both of us.

10:40.320 --> 10:41.720
It's no big deal. Come on.

10:42.680 --> 10:44.240
Just say it's from you.

10:44.320 --> 10:46.000
I hardly know him anyway.

10:46.880 --> 10:49.160
It's fine. Let's go together.

10:49.720 --> 10:51.160
We agreed to meet here.

10:53.040 --> 10:53.880
Welcome.

11:00.720 --> 11:02.000
Sang Zhi?

11:04.040 --> 11:05.240
Jiaxu.

11:05.320 --> 11:06.560
Are you hanging out with your friend?

11:07.240 --> 11:08.080
Hello.

11:08.160 --> 11:09.040
Hello.

11:10.080 --> 11:11.320
Do you work here?

11:14.320 --> 11:15.360
Here.

11:15.440 --> 11:16.640
See what you would like to eat.

11:16.720 --> 11:17.760
You can order here later.

11:17.840 --> 11:19.200
Find a table first.

11:25.000 --> 11:26.240
He's so handsome.

11:26.920 --> 11:27.920
Who is he?

11:28.000 --> 11:29.760
That doesn't look like your brother.

11:30.760 --> 11:32.040
He's my brother's friend.

11:32.120 --> 11:33.400
Your brother's friend?

11:37.760 --> 11:38.600
He's handsome.

11:38.680 --> 11:40.080
Your brother is handsome too.

11:40.160 --> 11:41.760
Sang Zhi, you're so lucky.

11:41.840 --> 11:43.280
See what you would like to eat.

11:46.440 --> 11:47.760
I want…

11:50.000 --> 11:51.240
Red beans

11:52.520 --> 11:53.920
or milk custard with mango.

11:55.520 --> 11:57.400
I think I'll get

11:57.480 --> 11:59.200
the milk custard with red beans.

12:02.120 --> 12:03.920
Saigon milk custard.

12:04.000 --> 12:05.280
I don't think I can eat this.

12:05.760 --> 12:08.480
I'll get the milk custard with red beans.

12:09.200 --> 12:10.520
Milk custard with red beans then.

12:10.600 --> 12:11.440
Have a look.

12:12.640 --> 12:13.800
I will have

12:14.880 --> 12:16.200
pearl sago with coconut milk.

12:16.280 --> 12:18.040
- Is that all?
- Yes.

12:18.560 --> 12:19.920
I'll go order.

12:20.000 --> 12:21.200
Keep an eye on my phone.

12:21.280 --> 12:22.160
Sure.

12:27.080 --> 12:28.320
What do you want to order?

12:28.400 --> 12:29.520
I want

12:30.080 --> 12:31.360
one milk custard with red beans

12:31.440 --> 12:33.160
and one pearl sago with coconut milk.

12:33.240 --> 12:34.080
Okay.

12:34.160 --> 12:35.440
Which one is yours?

12:36.080 --> 12:37.360
The pearl sago with coconut milk.

12:48.880 --> 12:50.200
You're one yuan short.

12:52.880 --> 12:53.880
No, I'm not.

12:55.200 --> 12:56.680
You stole so many glances at me.

12:57.360 --> 12:59.120
I can't let you do that for free.

13:03.400 --> 13:05.400
No wonder you have no customers.

13:05.480 --> 13:07.200
It's because you're running a shady shop.

13:09.000 --> 13:10.920
Only because I charged you an extra yuan?

13:11.000 --> 13:12.600
I didn't steal glances at you.

13:14.000 --> 13:16.240
Okay, I'm the one making stuff up.

13:17.600 --> 13:19.440
Would I really charge you?

13:19.520 --> 13:21.440
Keep it to buy yourself candy.

13:21.520 --> 13:22.640
No way.

13:22.720 --> 13:24.640
Don't you work here to make money?

13:24.720 --> 13:25.800
If I don't pay you,

13:25.880 --> 13:27.240
how will you make money?

13:29.720 --> 13:30.800
Take back the money.

13:31.440 --> 13:32.600
Treating you to dessert

13:32.680 --> 13:33.760
won't put me in the red.

13:34.360 --> 13:35.440
Your friend is waiting.

13:52.600 --> 13:54.920
Sang Zhi, is your brother's friend

13:55.000 --> 13:56.360
treating us to desserts?

13:58.760 --> 14:00.200
- Yes.
- That's great.

14:00.280 --> 14:02.080
I'm low on money after buying the gift.

14:04.240 --> 14:05.320
I'll ask the others.

14:06.560 --> 14:08.080
Where are you now?

14:12.200 --> 14:14.520
Where are you guys?
We've been waiting for a long time.

14:17.280 --> 14:19.200
Fu Zhengchu, hurry up.

14:19.880 --> 14:20.720
All right.

14:22.480 --> 14:23.440
Your milk custard.

14:25.120 --> 14:25.960
Thank you.

14:28.080 --> 14:29.000
Thank you, Jiaxu.

14:29.080 --> 14:30.120
Yours is hot.

14:34.120 --> 14:34.960
Try it.

14:38.720 --> 14:40.080
It smells so good.

14:41.880 --> 14:43.080
Do you want to try mine?

14:44.280 --> 14:45.160
Xiaoduan.

14:45.240 --> 14:46.160
Mr. Gao.

14:47.080 --> 14:49.000
I have to run to the second store.

14:49.080 --> 14:49.920
By the way,

14:50.400 --> 14:51.520
how about I give you

14:51.600 --> 14:53.600
half a month of your advance first?

14:54.400 --> 14:56.200
- Thank you, Mr. Gao.
- Okay, get back to work.

14:56.280 --> 14:58.160
- I'll take care of it.
- Okay.

15:07.040 --> 15:08.600
Does he keep working

15:09.840 --> 15:11.680
because he is short on cash?

15:16.440 --> 15:17.280
Fu Zhengchu!

15:17.360 --> 15:19.160
- Sang Zhi, sorry for being late.
- Hello.

15:21.520 --> 15:22.720
Hello!

15:23.800 --> 15:24.720
Hello.

15:29.200 --> 15:30.480
Sang Zhi.

15:30.560 --> 15:31.720
Does your brother work here?

15:33.960 --> 15:35.600
But isn't your family rich?

15:37.960 --> 15:39.480
Will you mind your own business?

15:44.760 --> 15:45.640
It's late.

15:45.720 --> 15:46.720
Let's go have fun.

15:47.600 --> 15:48.520
Let's go.

15:48.600 --> 15:49.800
We're not done yet.

15:50.440 --> 15:51.720
Stop eating, Sang Zhi.

15:51.800 --> 15:52.920
Let's go.

15:53.000 --> 15:54.440
Everyone is waiting for us.

15:54.520 --> 15:55.880
There is plenty of food there.

15:55.960 --> 15:56.880
Let's go.

15:59.120 --> 16:00.000
Sangsang, let's go.

16:00.080 --> 16:00.960
What are you thinking?

16:01.040 --> 16:02.440
Get ready. Hide.

16:05.000 --> 16:06.480
Are you going out with your friends?

16:08.520 --> 16:09.840
Be careful.

16:09.920 --> 16:11.440
Make sure to go home before dark.

16:12.080 --> 16:13.520
Leave her to us.

16:14.520 --> 16:16.320
- Have fun.
- Goodbye.

16:16.400 --> 16:17.280
- Bye.
- Bye.

16:19.120 --> 16:20.040
Let's go.

16:21.760 --> 16:22.600
Sangsang.

16:23.080 --> 16:24.320
Why does your brother's friend

16:24.400 --> 16:25.880
sound like my dad?

16:25.960 --> 16:27.920
My dad said the same thing before I left.

16:29.840 --> 16:31.360
We haven't hung out in a long while.

16:31.440 --> 16:32.920
Just the thought of it makes me happy.

16:33.000 --> 16:33.920
Wait, Zhenru.

16:34.000 --> 16:35.440
Give me a minute.

16:35.520 --> 16:36.880
Sangsang, where are you going?

16:37.560 --> 16:39.000
They're already waiting for us.

16:45.320 --> 16:46.200
Why did you come back?

16:52.600 --> 16:54.040
Jiaxu, are you short on cash?

16:57.120 --> 16:58.840
I heard from Sang Yan that you work.

16:59.440 --> 17:00.960
Then I see you working today.

17:02.560 --> 17:03.520
I wanted to say

17:03.600 --> 17:05.040
that you don't have to treat me

17:05.119 --> 17:06.920
if you're short on cash.

17:12.400 --> 17:14.880
I can afford to buy you dessert.

17:14.960 --> 17:16.160
Why are you worrying so much?

17:55.560 --> 17:57.200
This kid.

18:01.880 --> 18:04.320
- Happy birthday to you
- Happy birthday to you

18:04.960 --> 18:06.760
- Happy birthday to you
- Happy birthday to you

18:07.760 --> 18:10.120
- Happy birthday to you
- Happy birthday to you

18:12.160 --> 18:13.200
We wish you…

18:13.280 --> 18:15.120
- Health!
- Good luck!

18:15.200 --> 18:16.040
Great fortune,

18:16.120 --> 18:18.280
and a happy family!

18:19.040 --> 18:19.960
Enough.

18:20.040 --> 18:21.200
- Come on.
- Let's have cake.

18:21.280 --> 18:22.840
- Come on.
- Make a wish!

18:22.920 --> 18:23.840
Make a wish.

18:27.160 --> 18:28.400
Here. Make a wish.

18:33.320 --> 18:34.520
This is my wish.

18:41.280 --> 18:42.200
Sang Zhi--

18:42.280 --> 18:43.160
Wait.

18:44.320 --> 18:45.800
Do you have something to say to me?

18:46.360 --> 18:47.920
I have something to tell you.

18:48.000 --> 18:49.520
Is it okay

18:49.600 --> 18:50.680
if I go home first?

18:52.360 --> 18:54.320
I already spent your birthday with you

18:54.400 --> 18:55.720
and sang the birthday song.

18:55.800 --> 18:56.840
I really want to go home.

18:56.920 --> 18:58.240
- Bye.
- Wait.

18:58.320 --> 19:00.440
Carry on. Have fun!

19:00.520 --> 19:01.640
Sang Zhi!

19:01.720 --> 19:03.080
Fu Zhengchu, go after her.

19:03.680 --> 19:04.520
Quick.

19:04.600 --> 19:06.360
You guys can eat first. I'll be back.

19:06.440 --> 19:08.400
- We'll cut the cake when you're back.
- Go.

19:08.480 --> 19:09.520
Fu Zhengchu!

19:13.160 --> 19:14.480
It's Fu Zhengchu's birthday,

19:14.560 --> 19:15.600
but Sang Zhi left early.

19:16.080 --> 19:17.000
He won't be happy.

19:17.560 --> 19:20.000
Yin Zhenru, Sang Zhi is a lousy friend.

19:35.440 --> 19:36.360
Sang Zhi!

19:38.360 --> 19:39.520
Why did you follow me outside?

19:39.600 --> 19:40.640
Aren't you partying?

19:40.720 --> 19:42.520
I came out for some air.

19:44.000 --> 19:45.080
You get your air.

19:45.160 --> 19:46.440
I'm going home.

19:47.440 --> 19:48.720
Let me see you off.

19:50.320 --> 19:51.680
We know each other so well.

19:51.760 --> 19:53.120
You don't need to do that.

19:53.880 --> 19:54.760
Sang Zhi.

19:55.600 --> 19:56.800
I don't believe you can't tell.

19:58.760 --> 20:00.240
Can't tell what?

20:00.320 --> 20:01.360
I studied so hard

20:01.440 --> 20:03.000
to get into the same high school as you.

20:03.080 --> 20:03.960
Don't you know?

20:04.040 --> 20:04.920
I know.

20:05.000 --> 20:06.920
That's why I think you should

20:07.000 --> 20:08.240
focus on your studies.

20:08.320 --> 20:10.000
Why do you keep telling me to study?

20:11.600 --> 20:14.000
If, on the off chance,

20:15.520 --> 20:16.720
I have a crush on you,

20:16.800 --> 20:17.760
what would you think?

20:18.360 --> 20:19.440
I can't imagine it.

20:20.280 --> 20:21.840
No, what I mean is

20:22.320 --> 20:23.880
that you should think about

20:23.960 --> 20:25.240
how to study hard.

20:25.840 --> 20:26.960
Don't make jokes like this.

20:27.040 --> 20:28.960
I'm not joking with you.

20:29.600 --> 20:31.200
Have you forgotten that you knocked out

20:31.280 --> 20:32.840
one of my teeth when we were kids?

20:32.920 --> 20:34.400
That was years ago.

20:35.200 --> 20:36.480
Didn't I break my hand too?

20:39.640 --> 20:40.520
You're right.

20:41.000 --> 20:42.240
Well…

20:43.680 --> 20:44.600
Sang Zhi--

20:44.680 --> 20:45.680
No.

20:47.800 --> 20:49.520
Let's not talk about it.

20:49.600 --> 20:50.520
Sang Zhi!

20:50.600 --> 20:52.000
It's my birthday today.

20:52.600 --> 20:54.920
I chose today to tell you this.

20:55.000 --> 20:56.200
You're always doing this to me.

20:56.280 --> 20:59.280
- Couldn't you reject me another day?
- Why are you always like this?

20:59.360 --> 21:00.960
You start crying before even saying much.

21:01.040 --> 21:02.560
- You're always like this.
- I'm not.

21:02.640 --> 21:03.760
You're crying!

21:03.840 --> 21:06.560
What are you doing? Stop crying!

21:06.640 --> 21:09.280
Fu Zhengchu, why are you always--

21:09.360 --> 21:10.680
Am I interrupting?

21:10.760 --> 21:12.280
Sang Zhi's brother, hello.

21:13.200 --> 21:14.240
Goodbye.

21:24.440 --> 21:26.320
Jiaxu, were you eavesdropping?

21:26.880 --> 21:27.760
Yes.

21:30.120 --> 21:31.320
You sound so righteous.

21:32.160 --> 21:33.600
You're in high school.

21:33.680 --> 21:35.000
You can't date so early.

21:36.000 --> 21:36.920
I'm not.

21:37.840 --> 21:38.960
I'm not dating.

21:39.800 --> 21:40.640
Really.

21:40.720 --> 21:42.440
Weren't you eavesdropping?

21:42.520 --> 21:44.120
Didn't you hear me tell him

21:44.200 --> 21:45.440
to study hard

21:45.520 --> 21:46.880
and not think about other things?

21:47.880 --> 21:48.920
Come to think of it,

21:49.000 --> 21:51.640
it's normal to have these ideas
during adolescence.

21:52.240 --> 21:53.840
But your task now

21:53.920 --> 21:55.800
is to study hard and not get distracted.

21:55.880 --> 21:57.680
I told you I didn't.

21:59.800 --> 22:00.840
I really didn't.

22:04.200 --> 22:05.320
I trust you.

22:08.360 --> 22:09.280
But Sang Zhi,

22:10.080 --> 22:13.080
it's nice to have people who like you.

22:13.640 --> 22:15.240
You can thank him for liking you

22:15.720 --> 22:18.080
before gently rejecting him.

22:18.160 --> 22:19.520
But you can't hurt him.

22:22.120 --> 22:23.480
I didn't hurt him.

22:23.560 --> 22:25.400
I saw him crying.

22:27.560 --> 22:29.080
He was crying

22:29.160 --> 22:31.400
because he has always been a crybaby.

22:31.480 --> 22:32.680
He and I grew up fighting.

22:32.760 --> 22:33.960
He's always the first to cry.

22:34.640 --> 22:35.760
Fighting?

22:36.400 --> 22:37.440
No wonder your parents

22:37.520 --> 22:38.880
got called to school every day.

22:40.760 --> 22:42.240
It didn't happen every day.

22:42.320 --> 22:45.840
It was just a couple of times…

22:45.920 --> 22:47.400
Put out your hand.

22:54.480 --> 22:55.520
Take it back.

22:56.520 --> 22:58.640
Otherwise, people will say

22:58.720 --> 23:00.480
I extorted a high school student.

23:00.560 --> 23:01.760
It's not extortion.

23:02.840 --> 23:05.440
I had dessert. I should pay for it.

23:05.520 --> 23:07.320
What dessert costs this much?

23:07.920 --> 23:09.720
Do you really think this is a shady shop?

23:11.960 --> 23:12.960
Jiaxu.

23:16.640 --> 23:18.920
I just think it's a little hard for you

23:19.480 --> 23:20.840
to work multiple jobs

23:21.840 --> 23:23.320
because you're short on cash.

23:24.320 --> 23:26.200
If I can help you…

23:27.960 --> 23:29.640
But don't overthink it.

23:29.720 --> 23:31.440
If it were my brother,

23:31.520 --> 23:33.120
I would help him too.

23:33.800 --> 23:34.680
I swear.

23:39.400 --> 23:40.560
So do you feel bad

23:41.120 --> 23:42.240
for me?

23:43.160 --> 23:44.040
No.

23:50.480 --> 23:51.520
Sorry.

23:52.760 --> 23:53.880
Are you mad?

23:54.560 --> 23:55.640
I'm not.

24:00.080 --> 24:01.240
Thank you, Sang Zhi.

24:02.720 --> 24:04.520
You know you need to be nice to me now.

24:06.160 --> 24:08.640
I'm touched that you did this

24:08.720 --> 24:11.000
and the thought behind it.

24:12.080 --> 24:14.720
But I'm not that broke.

24:16.160 --> 24:17.440
How about this?

24:18.200 --> 24:19.480
When I'm so broke

24:19.560 --> 24:21.320
that I can't afford to feed myself,

24:21.400 --> 24:22.480
I'll borrow money from you.

24:23.120 --> 24:23.960
Okay?

24:31.200 --> 24:33.880
All right, I need to get back to work.

24:33.960 --> 24:36.240
Do you know how to get
to the nearest bus stop?

24:37.560 --> 24:38.560
Yes.

24:39.120 --> 24:40.320
Can you go home by yourself?

24:41.720 --> 24:42.640
Yes.

24:44.320 --> 24:45.200
Goodbye then.

25:16.480 --> 25:17.720
Zhenru.

25:17.800 --> 25:19.520
What's the teacher's main focus?

25:20.120 --> 25:21.000
It's this one.

25:21.840 --> 25:23.840
15th century BC.

25:23.920 --> 25:24.920
This question type.

25:27.040 --> 25:28.000
Zhenru.

25:36.000 --> 25:36.840
Zhenru.

25:37.680 --> 25:39.520
For Sports Day,
what event did you sign up for?

25:46.680 --> 25:47.800
The name list is ready.

25:47.880 --> 25:48.800
Look over here.

25:49.680 --> 25:51.200
The annual Sports Day

25:51.280 --> 25:52.520
is about to begin.

25:53.000 --> 25:55.160
This year, we have a lot of events.

25:55.240 --> 25:58.480
The school decided to hold it
at Nanwu University as usual.

25:58.560 --> 26:00.320
Is everyone participating?

26:00.400 --> 26:01.840
- Yes.
- Yes.

26:02.400 --> 26:03.360
Sang Zhi.

26:04.680 --> 26:06.320
Why don't I see your name?

26:08.520 --> 26:11.200
Sir, I'll be the record clerk this year.

26:11.280 --> 26:12.800
That's not a sport.

26:13.760 --> 26:14.920
You can do the high jump.

26:16.400 --> 26:17.600
I can't jump.

26:18.320 --> 26:19.360
I have bad knees.

26:21.040 --> 26:22.720
You're 17 years old,

26:23.200 --> 26:24.720
not 70!

26:25.400 --> 26:27.120
Knee problems at such a young age

26:27.200 --> 26:29.560
prove that you lack exercise.

26:30.200 --> 26:31.040
You're doing this.

26:33.080 --> 26:34.840
I'm scared I'll drag everyone down

26:34.920 --> 26:35.840
with this flaw.

26:35.920 --> 26:36.920
It doesn't matter.

26:37.880 --> 26:40.080
Participate and show what you can do.

26:40.160 --> 26:41.840
It doesn't matter whether you win.

26:42.440 --> 26:43.640
What matters is participation,

26:43.720 --> 26:44.880
not prizes.

26:45.560 --> 26:46.640
What do I want?

26:46.720 --> 26:48.840
I want you to be involved.

26:49.720 --> 26:50.840
It's you then.

26:53.320 --> 26:54.360
Also,

26:54.840 --> 26:56.920
go to the class monitor

26:57.000 --> 26:58.280
and report your clothing sizes.

26:58.760 --> 27:00.400
I'm going to order class uniforms.

27:00.960 --> 27:03.000
Sir, what is the style of the uniform?

27:04.200 --> 27:05.120
It's a secret.

27:07.680 --> 27:08.640
It will look very good.

27:09.320 --> 27:12.520
It carries the vitality
of 17-year-old students like you.

27:12.600 --> 27:14.200
- Really?
- Is that so?

27:14.280 --> 27:15.280
The 100 m race.

27:16.080 --> 27:16.960
Chen Liqiang.

27:18.120 --> 27:19.760
Train hard with your three classmates.

27:21.000 --> 27:21.920
Zhenru.

27:22.400 --> 27:23.240
Zhenru.

27:23.880 --> 27:26.040
Zhenru, where are you going?

27:26.120 --> 27:27.480
I'm going to the store.

27:27.560 --> 27:28.800
I'll go with you.

27:28.880 --> 27:30.400
What do you want to eat? It's my treat.

27:30.480 --> 27:31.360
No, thank you.

27:47.800 --> 27:48.920
Grade 11.

27:49.000 --> 27:50.760
Men's 100 m sprint.

27:50.840 --> 27:52.080
Ready.

27:52.160 --> 27:53.040
Get set.

27:55.880 --> 27:59.240
- Go!
- Go!

27:59.320 --> 28:00.720
- Go!
- Go!

28:00.800 --> 28:02.840
- Go!
- Go!

28:02.920 --> 28:04.560
- Go!
- Go!

28:04.640 --> 28:06.240
- Go!
- Go!

28:06.320 --> 28:09.040
- Go!
- Go!

28:09.720 --> 28:11.440
Fu Zhengchu, go! Fu Zhengchu!

28:18.960 --> 28:20.160
Grade 11 students participating

28:20.240 --> 28:21.680
in the women's high jump,

28:21.760 --> 28:23.880
please report
to the registration area immediately.

28:23.960 --> 28:25.800
Sang Zhi, it's your turn.

28:25.880 --> 28:27.520
- Let's go.
- Zhenru, it's Sang Zhi's turn.

28:27.600 --> 28:28.880
- Let's go.
- Let's go together.

28:28.960 --> 28:31.120
I'm not going. You girls go ahead. Bye.

28:31.200 --> 28:32.040
We'll leave first.

28:32.120 --> 28:33.120
Yes, right over there.

28:38.120 --> 28:39.040
Thank you.

28:39.120 --> 28:40.080
It's so good-looking.

28:41.040 --> 28:42.040
It looks nice.

28:42.120 --> 28:43.040
Sang Zhi.

28:48.080 --> 28:49.080
Good luck.

28:50.480 --> 28:51.320
Good luck.

28:52.520 --> 28:53.680
I'm going to accept my award.

29:02.480 --> 29:04.440
REGISTRATION AREA,
WOMEN'S HIGH JUMP QUALIFIER

29:04.520 --> 29:05.720
Number 26.

29:05.800 --> 29:07.400
Xie Jialu, okay.

29:10.200 --> 29:12.360
You're disqualified from the competition.

29:12.440 --> 29:14.440
- Go home.
- You're really annoying.

29:14.520 --> 29:16.360
You're not tall enough, 120 cm won't do.

29:16.440 --> 29:18.360
I'm already 155 cm. Here.

29:22.080 --> 29:23.600
Class 1, Sang…

29:24.080 --> 29:25.840
- Here.
- Sang Zhi.

29:29.080 --> 29:30.840
Here. Turn around. Let me see.

29:30.920 --> 29:32.280
- No.
- Turn around and show me.

29:32.360 --> 29:33.480
No.

29:33.560 --> 29:34.640
Turn around.

29:34.720 --> 29:35.800
Turn around.

29:35.880 --> 29:37.480
Turn around. Let me see.

29:40.400 --> 29:42.240
- What are you doing?
- It's a match!

29:42.320 --> 29:43.720
0155!

29:46.200 --> 29:48.440
Are you worried nobody knows
that you're 155 cm?

29:48.520 --> 29:49.920
- Seriously. Go.
- Sang Zhi.

29:50.400 --> 29:52.320
What event are you participating in?

29:54.480 --> 29:55.320
High jump.

29:55.400 --> 29:57.160
155 cm, participating in the high jump.

29:57.760 --> 29:59.240
The sunflower is cute.

30:00.440 --> 30:01.280
I didn't choose it.

30:01.360 --> 30:02.240
Do your best.

30:02.320 --> 30:03.360
Good luck, little demon!

30:07.800 --> 30:09.080
- It's hilarious!
- You're so loud.

30:09.160 --> 30:10.120
I was napping.

30:13.840 --> 30:15.560
- Go!
- Go!

30:28.280 --> 30:29.440
Wear a hat.

30:30.120 --> 30:31.080
Don't get sunburned.

30:35.120 --> 30:36.240
How is your warmup?

30:36.880 --> 30:37.880
Move more

30:37.960 --> 30:39.240
so you don't get a sprain later.

30:42.360 --> 30:44.480
GO

30:52.640 --> 30:53.960
What are you doing?

30:54.040 --> 30:55.520
Mom and Dad told me to take photos.

30:56.000 --> 30:57.880
Can't you take it when I look good?

30:57.960 --> 30:59.520
Why do you have to do it when I'm…

30:59.600 --> 31:02.600
You have to tell me when you look good
or I won't know.

31:02.680 --> 31:03.920
- Look at 155 cm here.
- Delete it.

31:04.000 --> 31:05.880
- Give it to me.
- Delete it.

31:05.960 --> 31:06.840
Don't touch it.

31:08.880 --> 31:10.600
Stop bullying my sister all the time.

31:10.680 --> 31:11.560
What do you mean?

31:13.880 --> 31:14.800
Did you hear that?

31:15.320 --> 31:17.240
My brother told you to stop bullying me.

31:18.440 --> 31:19.360
Who is your brother?

31:22.000 --> 31:22.960
What about it?

31:24.120 --> 31:26.080
Fine, you can have her.

31:26.160 --> 31:27.480
- Let me take some photos.
- Go away.

31:27.560 --> 31:29.160
Take a few photos. You're handsome.

31:30.120 --> 31:31.120
Fine, you can have her.

31:31.200 --> 31:32.400
- Give me back my camera.
- Look.

31:34.880 --> 31:36.040
Don't I look handsome?

31:36.120 --> 31:37.520
- Grade 11.
- Do you really think so?

31:37.600 --> 31:39.520
The women's high jump will begin soon.

31:39.600 --> 31:40.560
Okay, competition time.

31:40.640 --> 31:42.280
Do your best. You can do it.

31:49.240 --> 31:50.480
Good.

31:53.240 --> 31:55.440
Next, 0845.

31:56.200 --> 31:57.200
Mr. Chen,

31:57.280 --> 31:58.920
the middle school isn't involved.

31:59.000 --> 32:00.120
Why are you here?

32:00.200 --> 32:01.480
I'm here to watch and learn.

32:01.560 --> 32:03.680
The middle school's Sports Day
is next month.

32:04.760 --> 32:05.640
Mr. Ling.

32:06.200 --> 32:08.480
The high school is different this year.

32:08.560 --> 32:09.440
How is it different?

32:09.520 --> 32:10.800
Look at your class uniform.

32:10.880 --> 32:12.200
What a great scene.

32:13.400 --> 32:14.680
It's trendy and stylish.

32:14.760 --> 32:15.920
Most importantly,

32:16.000 --> 32:16.920
it's full of vitality.

32:17.000 --> 32:18.760
Look at who chose it.

32:20.080 --> 32:22.160
Next, number 0155,

32:22.240 --> 32:23.120
Sang Zhi.

32:27.280 --> 32:29.440
Starting height, 1.05 m.

32:30.000 --> 32:31.160
- Go!
- Go!

32:31.240 --> 32:32.240
- Go!
- Sang Zhi, good luck!

32:32.320 --> 32:34.400
- Go!
- Go!

32:34.480 --> 32:35.400
Go, Sang Zhi!

32:35.480 --> 32:36.560
Go!

32:36.640 --> 32:37.800
- Go, 0155!
- Good luck!

32:37.880 --> 32:39.200
- Go!
- Go!

32:39.680 --> 32:40.880
- Go!
- Go!

32:40.960 --> 32:42.360
- Go!
- Sang Zhi, good luck!

32:42.440 --> 32:44.080
- Go!
- Go, Sang Zhi!

32:47.040 --> 32:48.600
- Go!
- Go!

32:59.320 --> 33:00.600
If she had just jumped,

33:00.680 --> 33:01.880
she would've gotten over.

33:03.880 --> 33:05.000
What the heck?

33:06.160 --> 33:08.200
- Sang Zhi, go!
- Sang Zhi, lift your legs.

33:08.280 --> 33:09.800
- Do your best, Sang Zhi.
- Work on it.

33:10.360 --> 33:11.240
- Go!
- Go!

33:11.320 --> 33:15.080
- Go!
- Go!

33:15.160 --> 33:17.040
- Go!
- Go, Sang Zhi!

33:18.880 --> 33:19.880
- Go!
- Go!

33:23.640 --> 33:26.000
Jump. Don't grab the rod, little demon.

33:30.480 --> 33:32.200
- Sang Zhi, go!
- Go!

33:32.280 --> 33:33.280
- Sang Zhi!
- Good luck!

33:33.360 --> 33:34.920
- Go, Sang Zhi.
- Do your best, Sang Zhi!

33:35.000 --> 33:36.040
Go!

33:41.600 --> 33:43.240
- Go, Sang Zhi!
- Good luck, little demon!

33:43.320 --> 33:45.520
- Go!
- Go!

33:45.600 --> 33:46.840
Good luck. Do your best.

33:46.920 --> 33:48.240
- Sang Zhi, go!
- Go!

33:48.320 --> 33:51.080
- Go!
- Go!

33:51.160 --> 33:52.240
Go, Sang Zhi.

34:20.560 --> 34:21.639
Are you okay?

34:21.719 --> 34:23.159
- Here. Make way.
- Are you okay?

34:23.239 --> 34:24.719
Get up first. Come on.

34:24.800 --> 34:26.760
- Be careful.
- Three, two, one, go.

34:27.440 --> 34:28.679
- It hurts.
- What's wrong?

34:28.760 --> 34:30.120
- This hurts.
- It's likely sprained.

34:30.199 --> 34:32.280
Take Sang Zhi to the medical station.

34:32.360 --> 34:33.600
- Yes.
- Sure.

34:33.679 --> 34:34.719
I'll carry you. Get on.

34:36.159 --> 34:37.520
- Be careful.
- Be careful.

34:39.080 --> 34:40.040
Don't touch that leg.

34:40.840 --> 34:41.840
I don't…

34:42.960 --> 34:44.159
Let's go.

34:44.239 --> 34:45.600
Aren't you Sang Zhi's brother?

34:47.320 --> 34:48.400
Hello, sir.

34:49.800 --> 34:51.159
- This is…
- My dad.

34:53.480 --> 34:54.679
Let's go.

34:54.760 --> 34:56.159
- Go.
- Hurry.

34:56.239 --> 34:57.320
Is this your…

34:58.240 --> 34:59.520
- It's all your fault.
- My dad.

34:59.600 --> 35:00.440
I'm so sorry, sir.

35:00.520 --> 35:01.800
Seriously.

35:01.880 --> 35:03.320
Did you hurt your head or your leg?

35:03.400 --> 35:04.520
Am I that old to be your dad?

35:04.600 --> 35:05.880
Can you stop scolding me?

35:05.960 --> 35:07.960
- You've nagged me all day.
- You're so bad at jumping.

35:08.040 --> 35:09.560
You still insist on it. Gosh.

35:09.640 --> 35:10.920
- Okay, stop it.
- I'll tell Dad.

35:11.000 --> 35:12.720
Are you going to rat me out again?

35:12.800 --> 35:14.360
- Stop moving!
- Watch out for her leg.

35:14.440 --> 35:17.160
- I don't want you to carry me.
- How will you walk with a sprain?

35:17.240 --> 35:18.320
Put me down.

35:18.400 --> 35:19.840
- Stop moving.
- Let me carry her.

35:20.400 --> 35:21.880
Sure. You can carry her.

35:21.960 --> 35:23.120
Stop arguing. Watch out.

35:23.200 --> 35:24.040
- Okay.
- Be careful.

35:24.120 --> 35:25.040
- Here.
- Her leg.

35:26.840 --> 35:27.800
Are you okay?

35:27.880 --> 35:29.200
Why is the medical station empty?

35:29.280 --> 35:30.160
Take her there first.

35:30.240 --> 35:31.600
- I'll get someone.
- Okay.

35:33.920 --> 35:35.520
You still talk so much when you're hurt.

35:37.320 --> 35:38.720
XURI MIDDLE-HIGH SCHOOL,
TEMPORARY MEDICAL STATION

35:40.880 --> 35:41.920
Sit down first.

35:43.200 --> 35:44.120
Be careful.

35:49.400 --> 35:50.520
Don't touch that leg yet.

35:53.480 --> 35:55.120
Let me disinfect it for you first.

36:09.200 --> 36:10.360
It might hurt a little.

36:10.440 --> 36:11.440
Bear with it for a bit.

36:16.560 --> 36:17.440
Does it hurt?

36:20.400 --> 36:22.120
Hang in there. It will be over soon.

36:27.880 --> 36:29.320
You're so badly hurt.

36:30.760 --> 36:31.720
What about this hand?

36:47.120 --> 36:48.000
Does it hurt?

36:51.480 --> 36:53.040
Why are you looking at me like that?

36:53.120 --> 36:54.400
What's the matter?

36:59.000 --> 37:00.520
You're nice to me.

37:01.120 --> 37:02.400
Unlike my brother.

37:02.480 --> 37:03.760
All he does is yell at me.

37:05.000 --> 37:07.000
Do you think he isn't nice to you?

37:07.080 --> 37:08.280
He doesn't love me at all.

37:09.280 --> 37:10.160
He doesn't love you?

37:11.960 --> 37:13.320
Didn't you see

37:13.880 --> 37:15.480
how panicked he was when you fell?

37:16.040 --> 37:17.680
He rushed over and carried you in no time.

37:18.400 --> 37:19.760
He doesn't love you?

37:20.600 --> 37:22.720
What's going on in your little head?

37:24.840 --> 37:27.040
But he's always yelling at me.

37:27.120 --> 37:29.200
I'm already hurt,
but he is still yelling at me.

37:29.280 --> 37:30.920
It's an impossible task

37:31.480 --> 37:32.640
to make him stop yelling.

37:34.040 --> 37:35.080
It's all done.

37:35.160 --> 37:36.000
Be careful

37:37.000 --> 37:37.920
with these wounds.

37:38.000 --> 37:38.880
Don't touch them.

37:39.800 --> 37:41.120
Don't get water on them.

37:42.520 --> 37:43.880
How are the wounds?

37:44.520 --> 37:46.080
I've treated the abrasions.

37:46.600 --> 37:48.640
But you had best take her to the hospital

37:48.720 --> 37:50.120
to check the sprain.

37:50.200 --> 37:51.480
Sure. Have a drink first.

37:53.080 --> 37:54.240
Here.

37:59.600 --> 38:01.440
Drink up. We'll go to the hospital.

38:05.480 --> 38:06.840
By the way, hold onto the camera.

38:08.040 --> 38:08.880
Here. Get on.

38:16.040 --> 38:18.080
Your brother has a class in the afternoon.

38:18.160 --> 38:19.960
Only your dad can take you
to the hospital.

38:24.120 --> 38:26.000
I beg of you.

38:27.160 --> 38:29.320
I'll also have to drop you off at school.

38:29.400 --> 38:30.600
How troublesome.

38:31.520 --> 38:32.680
It's fine.

38:32.760 --> 38:35.280
If your dad can't take you to school,

38:35.360 --> 38:36.200
I'll do it.

38:38.640 --> 38:39.920
Listen to your brother.

38:43.480 --> 38:44.400
Get on.

38:45.200 --> 38:46.040
Be careful.

38:46.560 --> 38:47.600
Be careful.

38:48.280 --> 38:49.520
Don't strangle me.

38:49.600 --> 38:50.840
I'll leave you to it.

38:57.880 --> 38:58.800
Let's go.

38:59.400 --> 39:00.320
Wait.

39:00.840 --> 39:01.880
- Why?
- Wait.

39:01.960 --> 39:02.800
Wait.

39:03.840 --> 39:04.840
I can't see.

39:04.920 --> 39:07.520
Help her up first. Be careful.

39:11.560 --> 39:12.920
Proceed with the competition.

39:16.040 --> 39:17.320
- Be careful.
- What are you doing?

39:22.920 --> 39:23.920
Be careful.

39:30.560 --> 39:35.240
XURI MIDDLE-HIGH SCHOOL,
TEMPORARY MEDICAL STATION

39:51.400 --> 39:52.640
He's nice.

39:53.920 --> 39:55.320
He's very nice to me.

39:56.960 --> 40:00.360
But he seems to be nice to everyone.

40:02.200 --> 40:04.160
I'm not the most special one.

40:13.400 --> 40:15.400
Well, that's all for my class today.

40:15.480 --> 40:16.360
Class dismissed.

40:18.040 --> 40:18.960
Sang Zhi, bye.

40:19.040 --> 40:19.880
Bye.

40:30.040 --> 40:31.120
Hello?

40:31.200 --> 40:32.560
Hello, little demon.

40:32.640 --> 40:34.080
Duan Jiaxu will pick you up today.

40:34.800 --> 40:36.760
He will be there in about 20 minutes.

40:36.840 --> 40:37.680
Wait for him.

40:41.160 --> 40:42.200
Got it.

40:42.280 --> 40:44.600
Also, be good.

40:44.680 --> 40:46.200
Don't cause him trouble.

40:46.280 --> 40:48.240
When have I caused him trouble?

40:49.160 --> 40:51.240
All right, I'm just saying.

40:51.320 --> 40:53.000
I have to go. Bye.

40:55.720 --> 40:57.600
Why would I cause him trouble?

41:05.600 --> 41:06.880
Sang Zhi.

41:08.640 --> 41:11.760
Can you come with me to buy something?

41:38.480 --> 41:40.080
I'm not going to tell Mom and Dad.

41:40.160 --> 41:41.080
They're at work.

41:41.160 --> 41:42.360
Coming here would be a hassle.

41:45.880 --> 41:47.360
I already helped you take the day off.

41:47.440 --> 41:48.280
Don't worry.

41:53.040 --> 41:54.240
Here. Hold on tight.

41:56.760 --> 41:57.720
Look at what this is.

42:05.040 --> 42:06.120
I'll unwrap one for you.

42:08.360 --> 42:09.320
Here.

42:25.560 --> 42:27.120
So

42:28.720 --> 42:31.280
did you purposely leave
to buy me some candy?

42:33.080 --> 42:34.000
You wish.

42:34.080 --> 42:35.520
I went to buy water for Duan Jiaxu.

42:35.600 --> 42:36.720
I got one for you in passing.

42:39.720 --> 42:40.880
It was all your fault today.

42:42.280 --> 42:43.720
You call me ugly every day

42:43.800 --> 42:45.760
- and I don't complain.
- That's different.

42:45.840 --> 42:46.680
How so?

42:46.760 --> 42:47.880
I'm speaking the truth.

42:51.400 --> 42:52.240
Go!

42:52.880 --> 42:53.880
I'm not a horse!
